attorneys: Motion of Special Master for allowance of fees and disbursements is granted, and the Special Master is awarded a total of $50,933.89, for the period January 1, 2017, through February 28, 2017, to be paid equally by the parties.
casebody.head_matter:
FLORIDA, plaintiff,
v.
GEORGIA.
No. 142, Original.
Supreme Court of the United States
April 3, 2017.
Motion of Special Master for allowance of fees and disbursements is granted, and the Special Master is awarded a total of $50,933.89, for the period January 1, 2017, through February 28, 2017, to be paid equally by the parties.
